data.description: Looking for the perfect mix of space, easy living and convenience? Look no further than this home situated on a 1.5-acre plot of land in the wonderful Lakeside school district! This home offers a metal roof, a massive koi pond filled with koi, renovated new flooring, a shed with studs up ready to be converted into an in-law suite, and a partially finished area that is ready for drywall to be put up that will increase this home to a 4 bedroom and add an extra 200 SQFT -/+! Agents see Remarks
